4:
Sera, we've seen plants like this in
the archive before. Do you
remember?
12:
I suppose you never were that
interested in this kind of thing. It'd be
more surprising if you did remember.
19:
Attention, everyone. Our itinerary for
the day is accompanying Dez
through town. Are you prepared?
23:
What do we gotta be prepared for?
We're on vacation—what's the worst
that can happen?
28: Do not say I did not warn you!
31:
Ahaha, I don't mean to cause such
trouble. You're free to do whatever
you like instead.
34:
We've seen our fair share of
hardships. I promise WE have the
stamina to accompany you for as
long as you wish.
38:
Commander Light. It is arrogant of
you to assume that you can
accompany Dez for longer than I.
43:
This calls for a competition. May
whoever is the better tourist win!
47:
By the way, Dez, where specifically
did you wanna go?
50:
Oh, I don't have any specific
destinations in mind. I was thinking
of going around the entire island at
least five times or so.
60:
Once again, I have underestimated
Dez's information processing speed.
64:
My own memory is at its limit. I
cannot process any more...
67:
I have also been separated from the
group. It is hazardous to disrupt
squad formation...
76:
Is that you, Stella? I am afraid I
require some rest.
82:
...So you have also lost track of
everyone else.
86:
Everyone disappeared while I was
looking at ice cream.
94:
I am. However, I believe I should take
it easy for a little while.
97:
Allowing Dez to roam free was a
mistake. I have now lost the
competition as well.
105:
By the by... Stella, what are you
holding?
116:
Ah. I nearly forgot this body is
equipped with tasting and digestive
functions. Are you truly all right with
sharing?
120: Of course. Here, it's sweet and tasty.
126:
I-is this... what sweetness tastes like?
It is marvelous...
134:
I would like to be good friends with
Dez, but I am not sure if this is how a
friendship should be. Do you have
any suggestions?
138:
A-actually, never mind! Please
forget that I asked. My apologies for
wasting your time.
142:
That's a difficult question... that
doesn't have just one answer.
145:
Relationships are hard. And they are
also not simple.
148:
But from my point of view, you and
Dez look like you're having fun when
you're together.
152:
Hehehe. If that is the case, then I
definitely know I am having fun
when I am with you, Stella.
161:
It is the same with Alk, Nimbus, and
Commander Light. I enjoy spending
time with everyone.
165:
That means that... I am friends with
you all.
168:
I am filled with joy at the
thought—enough that I would never
wish to be deleted...
177:
Thank you, Stella. I believe I know
how to tackle the problem now!
181:
We should regroup with the others.
Are you finished with your ice cream?
185: I am. We can head out.
195:
Ah, I'm sorry. You said I could go
wherever I wanted, so I may have
gone overboard...
199:
S-Sera... I won... the competition...
correct?
203:
Were you seriously competing this
whole time...
208:
Yes, you won. I should have known
that you would have no trouble
marching with Dez, Commander.
211:
I definitely went overboard,
considering you had to pull out your
jets to try to keep up.
213:
As an apology, take this. I thought
it'd look good on you. What do you
think?
217:
Ha... Hahaha! You may have left me
behind today, but soon, you will be
the one keeping up!
221:
I have already acquired the
knowledge necessary to treat you
all to an even better tourist
experience!
224:
Prepare yourselves—I will not be
taken lightly!
228:
Uh... We're all headed back to the
same hotel. Is she gonna be like this
for the rest of the day?
232:
It's fine. She had a smile on her face
as she blasted off.
